Content:

I don't know if it's even worth correcting her, but this isn't true. They were about a day away from closing a funding round when Google got interested.

Author: waleedka
Content: What I found interesting was that he's been working on this startup for about 5 years now, and just recently made an "overnight" success. It enforces what I'm starting to realize that those companies that explode all of a sudden are not just lucky, but they probably work for years experimenting with different models an failing, and then failing again, until they finally find something that works. It's encouraging and discouraging at the same time.
